         </p>
       </div>
       
       <div class="text-center">
         <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
           <span class="text-xl">ü§ù</span>
         </div>
         <h3 class="font-semibold text-accent mb-2">3. Community First</h3>
