         </p>
       </div>
       
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-warning/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-xl">üíù</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-warning mb-2">6. Donation-powered</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">
          Shomp is powered by donations. Your generous contributions make our work of serving creators with a community-centric marketplace possible. Donations are optional, you will be asked at checkout to include a contribution with your purchase. While not required, we really appreciate you helping the platform survive.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-3">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-info/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-xl">üåü</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-info mb-2">Join Our Mission</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">
          Support US artists and creatives by using Shomp for your digital product needs, or contribute to our nonprofit mission through donations.
        </p>
      </div>
       
     </div>
   </div>
 </div>

 <!-- Call to Action -->
 <div class="py-16 bg-primary text-primary-content">
   <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
     <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Start Selling?</h2>
    <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
      Join creators who are ready to take control of their earnings
    </p>
     <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
       <a href="/dashboard/products/new" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
         Start Selling
       </a>
       <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg text-primary-content border-primary-content hover:bg-primary-content hover:text-primary">
         Learn More
       </a>
     </div>
   </div>
 </div>

